attributes.name: Mahogany Wall Shelf
attributes.description: This shelf is perfect for displaying your most expensive violin. You have one of those, right?

attributes.name: Maple Armoire
attributes.description: If you shut yourself into this armoire on a quiet night, you might be able to hear the wood around you resonate with the music of the cosmos.

attributes.name: Maple Cabinet
attributes.description: There is a custom on Aeternum that a young woodsman must use his own two hands to make a cabinet out of the first tree he ever fells.

attributes.name: Maple Chest of Drawers
attributes.description: This maple chest of drawers will keep your collection safe and sound. What collection? Any collection!

attributes.name: Maple Dresser
attributes.description: To make a maple dresser of this quality, the artisan must completely clear their mind of all thoughts. Then, they say, the dresser makes itself.

attributes.name: Maple Large Bookcase
attributes.description: The same wood that went into this bookcase is also used by luthiers to craft Aeternum's finest musical instruments.

attributes.name: Maple Small Bookcase
attributes.description: There's no finer place to store all your old sea maps and star charts. You won't be needing them here on Aeternum.

attributes.name: Maple Wall Shelf
attributes.description: This maple shelf calls out for something soft and comforting, like your favorite stuffed animal.

attributes.name: Narrow Ebony Bookcase
attributes.description: This bookcase was made before books were even invented.

attributes.name: Narrow Jade Bookcase
attributes.description: You'll retain 10% more information from books stored in a jade bookcase.

attributes.name: Narrow Rosewood Bookcase
attributes.description: Books with upsetting covers can go in the drawers.

attributes.name: Narrow Teak Bookcase
attributes.description: Each shelf has a handy railing so your books won't fall off the back.

attributes.name: Oak Armoire
attributes.description: An immortal owner needs an immortal place to store their clothes. The oak armoire is sturdy enough to withstand the ravages of both time and small explosions.

attributes.name: Oak Cabinet
attributes.description: You can't just hide your secrets in any old cabinet. There's a saying on Aeternum: 'oak never tells'.

attributes.name: Oak Chest of Drawers
attributes.description: What's inside the drawers isn't important. What really matters is that you did your best.

attributes.name: Oak Dresser
attributes.description: Oak wood is associated with the king of gods in many mythic traditions. Your socks and underwear deserve nothing less.

attributes.name: Oak Large Bookcase
attributes.description: This bookcase is sturdy enough to hold all your hopes and dreams for the future.

attributes.name: Oak Small Bookcase
attributes.description: This oak bookcase is perfect for displaying your favorite flowers, for a bright pop of color and a soothing fragrance.

attributes.name: Oak Wall Shelf
attributes.description: Oak trees are the most likely to be hit by lightning. Luckily, this shelf is specially insulated.

attributes.name: Open Rickety Bookcase
attributes.description: Lots of space to place all kinds of things, it doesn’t always have to be books.

attributes.name: Painted Ebony Chest
attributes.description: If you put your ear to this chest, you might hear the echoes of many years of domestic bliss.

attributes.name: Painted Jade Chest
attributes.description: The artist developed a special type of paint that adheres to jade without damaging it.

attributes.name: Painted Rosewood Chest
attributes.description: The dragons painted on the doors of this chest will protect its contents from the outside world.

attributes.name: Painted Teak Chest
attributes.description: This beautiful teak chest is equally good at storing silks and snacks.

attributes.name: Rickety Wooden Wall Shelf
attributes.description: The beauty is not in the shelf itself, but in the possibilities it contains.

attributes.name: Rosewood Apothecary Cabinet
attributes.description: With this fine cabinet in your house, don't be surprised if your neighbors start coming to you for medical advice.

attributes.name: Rosewood Circular Curio Shelf
attributes.description: This shelf might look dainty and delicate, but it can hold a great deal of heavy items and still remain on the wall.

attributes.name: Rosewood Dresser
attributes.description: The red color invites joy; the chrysanthemum drawer pulls denote longevity. With this dresser, you'll be happy forever.

attributes.name: Rosewood Pedestal Shelf
attributes.description: The perfect place to display a priceless family heirloom, or perhaps an interesting rock you found on your morning walk.

attributes.name: Rustic Wooden Scrollcase
attributes.description: Full of cubbies for all your paper, vellum, and papyrus. Clay tablets, too, if you're into the classics.

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Galley Shelf
attributes.description: You can store your balsamic vinegar on this shelf without worrying about ruining the finish.

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Low Bookcase
attributes.description: The finish might been washed off this bookcase by the hard salt sea, but it still holds just as much knowledge as ever.

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Scrolled Armoire
attributes.description: Every crack in the wood of this armoire tells a story of the high seas.

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Short Dresser
attributes.description: The little skull-shaped drawer-pulls on this dresser are surprisingly charming.

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Tall Bookcase
attributes.description: The wood is worn, but the brass hardware looks brand new. Was this bookcase deliberately roughed up?

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Tall Dresser
attributes.description: You might need a ladder to reach those top drawers. That's where you'll hide the good stuff.

attributes.name: Salt-stripped Vanity Table
attributes.description: Place this handsome vanity table near your front door, to make sure your hat looks good before you leave.

attributes.name: Small Rustic Cabinet
attributes.description: Perfect for a very organized person. A place for everything, and everything in its place.

attributes.name: Teak Apothecary Cabinet
attributes.description: Keep your wits sharp by trying to remember what you put in all these drawers.

attributes.name: Teak Circular Curio Shelf
attributes.description: A beautiful display for your smallest treasures, netsukes, tchotchkes, trinkets, gewgaws, knickknacks, bric-a-brac, or whatever is closest to your heart.
